Package: LeastFracDiff
Type: Package
Title: Grid Search for the Least Fractional Differenciation Order
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Luis Damiano <damiano.luis@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Luis Damiano <damiano.luis@gmail.com>
Description: Minimal tools for approximating the least fractional difference order that transforms a time series into a stationary one, as suggested by de Prado (2018).
